1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 9=

11
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,399
Don't hurt him.

12
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:06,760
Baby.

13
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:07,680
Where're you?

14
00:01:07,799 --> 00:01:08,879
Come catch me!

15
00:01:10,079 --> 00:01:10,319
Coming.

16
00:01:10,319 --> 00:01:10,959
Over here.

17
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,000
Got you.

18
00:01:12,959 --> 00:01:13,280
Come on.

19
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:25,959
Give me a drink.

20
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:33,799
Where're you?

21
00:01:34,519 --> 00:01:35,120
Why did you go?

22
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:40,879
Another beauty.

23
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,879
Congratulations, Mr. Gu.

24
00:01:44,959 --> 00:01:47,640
After tonight, the Lin family will be
in your hands.

25
00:01:53,439 --> 00:01:55,079
Once I flatten the whole city,

26
00:01:55,959 --> 00:01:57,560
I'll take each of you as my wife.

27
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,079
Hey,

28
00:01:59,599 --> 00:02:01,519
if you take all of us home,

29
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,799
then I'll have to be the official wife.

30
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:07,280
You're quite the charmer.

31
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:08,879
Don't worry.

32
00:02:09,319 --> 00:02:10,879
You won't be left out tonight.

33
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:11,840
You're so bad.

34
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,319
Bring him in.

35
00:02:20,479 --> 00:02:20,759
Yes.

36
00:02:23,039 --> 00:02:24,120
Business comes first.

37
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:24,800
Sorry.

38
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:28,560
Mr. Gu.

39
00:02:29,479 --> 00:02:30,199
Mr. Gu.

40
00:02:30,639 --> 00:02:31,599
Chairman Lin Hai...

41
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:32,840
No.

42
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,520
Now you've become

43
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:36,639
the head of the Lin Group.

44
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:38,960
Mr. Gu...

45
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:40,280
that...

46
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:41,879
that thing...

47
00:02:41,879 --> 00:02:42,800
I didn't get it.

48
00:02:44,159 --> 00:02:44,680
Say that again.

49
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,199
What?

50
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:49,039
You didn't take care of Su Wubing.

51
00:02:49,439 --> 00:02:50,879
He ruined our whole plan.

52
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,000
Come on.

53
00:02:53,919 --> 00:02:55,000
Louder. Come on.

54
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:59,759
You didn't take care of Su Wubing...

55
00:03:02,439 --> 00:03:03,639
Mr. Gu...

56
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,639
You didn't get the item,

57
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,159
and now you're blaming me?

58
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:07,759
No, Mr. Gu.

59
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,879
As long as we cooperate,

60
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,840
we'll get the formula next time.

61
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,000
Lin Hai.

62
00:03:17,879 --> 00:03:19,800
What makes you think
you're qualified to work with me?

63
00:03:20,759 --> 00:03:21,039
I...

64
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:25,159
I'm still Lin Rong's own brother.

65
00:03:27,599 --> 00:03:28,240
Hai.

66
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:31,159
You're nothing more than
a lackey I keep.

67
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,840
You lick the boots

68
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,879
of whoever feeds you.

69
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:35,639
No, Mr. Gu...

70
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:36,919
Even if I didn't succeed,

71
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:38,080
I still put in the work.

72
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:43,680
Get lost.

73
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:47,840
Useless trash.

74
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:54,280
I didn't expect Su Wubing
to be so lucky.

75
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,800
It's fine, Mr. Gu.

76
00:03:57,360 --> 00:04:00,080
He can't dodge every bullet.

77
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,159
Were you and Su Wubing

78
00:04:03,759 --> 00:04:04,879
college classmates?

79
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,000
He chased you back then, right?

80
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,840
That's all in the past.

81
00:04:10,319 --> 00:04:12,080
Right now,

82
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,479
I'm focused on you.

83
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:16,319
But I need you

84
00:04:16,319 --> 00:04:18,639
to shift your focus to him.

85
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,079
Seduce him.

86
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,600
Then I'll naturally

87
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:22,959
get their secret formula.

88
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,720
By refining part of
Ye Xiaonuan's Cold Marrow,

89
00:04:43,879 --> 00:04:44,959
I opened up my meridians.

90
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,639
Even though I still can't break
Ningxue's curse,

91
00:04:47,879 --> 00:04:49,800
I can at least transfer
some spiritual power to her

92
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,560
and extend her life by three months.

93
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:30,839
Su Wubing...

94
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,160
Are you okay?

95
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,079
I didn't expect

96
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,040
your curse would actually

97
00:05:39,199 --> 00:05:40,519
absorb spiritual power.

98
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:41,759
What?

99
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:46,480
Su Wubing! Su Wubing!

100
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,120
Ningxue.

101
00:06:27,279 --> 00:06:27,680
Ningxue.

102
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:29,639
Ningxue.

103
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:42,639
Yesterday you were injured,

104
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:44,000
so I let you sleep here.

105
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:49,920
Also...

106
00:06:51,199 --> 00:06:53,639
what is the "curse" you mentioned

107
00:06:53,639 --> 00:06:54,439
before you passed out?

108
00:06:55,839 --> 00:06:57,240
And when you crushed the marriage,

109
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,720
you said something
about restoring memories.

110
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,120
Does it have anything to do with me?

111
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,040
When the time is right,

112
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,279
you'll understand everything.

113
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,600
Get up and keep training.

114
00:07:35,879 --> 00:07:36,439
Yingying.

115
00:07:37,279 --> 00:07:38,000
We give up.

116
00:07:38,439 --> 00:07:40,360
The three of us are no match for you.

117
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,279
Is it enough just to give up?

118
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,360
Slacking off again.

119
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,680
You're embarrassing us.

120
00:07:46,399 --> 00:07:47,240
Keep training.

121
00:07:50,399 --> 00:07:50,800
Yingying.

122
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:54,480
Ningxue.

123
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,160
What's wrong?

124
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,000
You seem upset.

125
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:05,160
I want to talk to you about Su Wubing.

126
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:15,920
Su Wubing isn't that simple.

127
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:17,600
He must have another purpose.

128
00:08:19,319 --> 00:08:20,920
If he really has an agenda,

129
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,839
why would he help me so much?

130
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:25,279
Men are all good at pretending.

131
00:08:25,639 --> 00:08:26,959
Back when he was here,

132
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:28,360
he was just a handyman.

133
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,920
Who would've thought
he was that skilled?

134
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:34,639
Every time I get close to him,

135
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:36,720
I get

136
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,320
this familiar feeling.

137
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,159
But I just can't remember.

138
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:46,799
Don't tell me you've fallen for him.

139
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:52,559
You're the Lin family's heiress.

140
00:08:52,559 --> 00:08:54,039
He's just a lowly handyman.

141
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:56,720
Besides, men are all the same.

142
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,159
He's definitely up to something.

143
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:01,720
Then why would he save my father
for no reason

144
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:04,279
and even offend Gu Yuanbing
for our family?

145
00:09:04,639 --> 00:09:05,759
What would he gain from that?

146
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:07,919
It's obviously to win your trust.

147
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:12,639
I don't know...

148
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,440
Still don't believe me?

149
00:09:15,279 --> 00:09:16,639
At the teahouse before,

150
00:09:16,639 --> 00:09:17,679
he was that skilled.

151
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:20,279
Then suddenly he's so weak
he has to go to the Herbal Hall.

152
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:22,159
Isn't that obvious acting?

153
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,399
But

154
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,159
don't worry.

155
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,879
What's your plan now?

156
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:37,759
Make him drop the act himself.

157
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,960
Spiritual power can slowly recover,

158
00:10:02,759 --> 00:10:04,080
but the curse of the Heavenly Dao...

159
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,200
Fan City Hotel, Room 2243.

160
00:10:14,279 --> 00:10:15,759
Urgent situation. Come immediately.

161
00:10:15,759 --> 00:10:16,200
No calls.

162
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,200
Why would

163
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,879
Ningxue suddenly asked me
to meet at a hotel?

164
00:10:21,639 --> 00:10:22,000
Not good.

165
00:10:47,407 --> 00:10:51,510
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

166
00:10:51,510 --> 00:10:56,230
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

167
00:10:56,230 --> 00:11:01,110
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

168
00:11:01,110 --> 00:11:06,230
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

169
00:11:06,230 --> 00:11:10,630
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

170
00:11:10,630 --> 00:11:15,310
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

171
00:11:15,310 --> 00:11:20,710
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

172
00:11:20,710 --> 00:11:27,104
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪
